{"tid":1860202,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［科學救港］含氯消毒劑製造器","createTime":"2020-02-03T13:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T05:27:33.000Z","uid":257601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52193875cfd91d2d3be06a4a4dcdbcd7a7346235","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"見到有人開始Sell次氨酸製做機就分享一下Chem佬吾會陌生嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n首先要有電解池(Electrolytic cell),<br />\n惰性電極(Inert electrodes)例如石墨Graphite,<br />\n電解濃鹽水(Electrolysis of concentrated NaCl(aq)),<br />\n因為有濃度效應(Concentration effect)，可以系電解池陽極收集氯氣(Collecting Cl2(g) at the Cathode of electrolytic cell),<br />\n將收集得黎嘅氯氣同電解水溶液混合:<br />\nCl2(g) + NaOH(aq) &lt;&gt; NaCl(aq) + NaOCl(aq)<br />\n就得到 次氨酸鈉水溶液 NaOCl(aq)<br />\n<br />\n又或者將收集得黎嘅氯氣同清水混合:<br />\nCl2(g) + H2O(l) &lt;&gt; HCl(aq) + HOCl(aq)<br />\n就得到次氨酸水溶液 HOCl(aq)<br />\n<br />\nNaOCl次氯酸鈉濃度需要達到200ppm至500ppm先有消毒效果，亦即等於1:99至1:49氨漂白水。<br />\n<br />\nHOCl次氯酸濃度就要達到5ppm至20ppm就得，消毒時間亦都快幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n至於點去量化(Quantify)你製作出黎嘅消毒劑，就快考DSE嘅你有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c947d40c7c85d19a74b711a4fdd87b3c01faa88f","tid":1860202,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"點先可以有效收集到Cl gas?"},{"pid":"456fff060edfe1f65f8b76b2568038012e20d90b","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c947d40c7c85d19a74b711a4fdd87b3c01faa88f","tid":1860202,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"點先可以有效收集到Cl gas?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"氨氣嘅密度比空氣高，所以儀器設計上要多花心思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ee992a93316aa2c3133a88dd1da9bb9694bdfd","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456fff060edfe1f65f8b76b2568038012e20d90b","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c947d40c7c85d19a74b711a4fdd87b3c01faa88f","tid":1860202,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"點先可以有效收集到Cl gas?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"氨氣嘅密度比空氣高，所以儀器設計上要多花心思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"氯*"},{"pid":"aab6c75f53c0226d9febfb9d8f923a63da60aef8","tid":1860202,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"我諗緊買vodka喺屋企做蒸餾可唔可行，好似易d"},{"pid":"0fd04ac46eb6a50b8c8c474a06d563c558807635","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://forum.babyhome.com.tw/files.forum.babyhome.com.tw/subject/4709239/sb_8rDEkBfyRzoA310V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.babyhome.com.tw%2Ffiles.forum.babyhome.com.tw%2Fsubject%2F4709239%2Fsb_8rDEkBfyRzoA310V.jpg&h=dbc36c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實好易整，又低成本。可惜用吾到係皮膚。"},{"pid":"a4f82449b76f2df591a28472eb1281d3bf511234","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fd04ac46eb6a50b8c8c474a06d563c558807635","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://forum.babyhome.com.tw/files.forum.babyhome.com.tw/subject/4709239/sb_8rDEkBfyRzoA310V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.babyhome.com.tw%2Ffiles.forum.babyhome.com.tw%2Fsubject%2F4709239%2Fsb_8rDEkBfyRzoA310V.jpg&h=dbc36c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實好易整，又低成本。可惜用吾到係皮膚。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"經調配後嘅次氯酸可以掂皮膚但次氯酸鈉吾可以"},{"pid":"f3f83914a586ba7c47752b54ae83db5cbe67f97c","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52193875cfd91d2d3be06a4a4dcdbcd7a7346235","tid":1860202,"uid":257601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T